                <fr:title text="Structural sheaf on spectra">Structural sheaf on spectra</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
  For a distributive lattice <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex>, the structural sheaf <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {O}_{D}]]></fr:tex> on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} D]]></fr:tex> is given as follows: For each <fr:link href="/idem-comm-CU42/" title="Zariski topology" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-CU42/" display-uri="idem-comm-CU42" type="local">basic open</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[O_p]]></fr:tex> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} D]]></fr:tex>, which we may simply write as <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p]]></fr:tex>, we define
  <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ \mathcal {O}_{D}(p) := D/p. ]]></fr:tex>
  For <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[q \le  p]]></fr:tex>, we put the restriction map to be
  <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ q \wedge  - : \mathcal {O}_{D}(p) \cong  D/p \twoheadrightarrow  D/q \cong  \mathcal {O}_{D}(q). ]]></fr:tex></html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors />
                <fr:date>
                  <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
                  <fr:month>6</fr:month>
                  <fr:day>8</fr:day>
                </fr:date>
                <fr:uri>https://charloced.github.io/schm-B6QO/</fr:uri>
                <fr:display-uri>schm-B6QO</fr:display-uri>
                <fr:route>/schm-B6QO/</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="Stalk for structural sheaf">Stalk for structural sheaf</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Remark</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
  If <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {O}_{D}]]></fr:tex> is a sheaf, then at each prime filter <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x\in \operatorname {Spec} D]]></fr:tex>, the stalk of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {O}_{D}]]></fr:tex> at <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x]]></fr:tex> is given by
  <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ \mathcal {O}_{D,x} \cong  \operatorname {colim}_{p\in  x}D/p \cong  D/x. ]]></fr:tex>
  As a distributive lattice this is <fr:link href="/idem-comm-75C1/" title="Local distributive lattice" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-75C1/" display-uri="idem-comm-75C1" type="local">local</fr:link> by <fr:link href="/idem-comm-EV8L/" title="Quotient of prime filters are local" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-EV8L/" display-uri="idem-comm-EV8L" type="local">Proposition <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-EV8L/" display-uri="idem-comm-EV8L" /></fr:link>.
</html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors />
                <fr:date>
                  <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
                  <fr:month>6</fr:month>
                  <fr:day>8</fr:day>
